00:13:01,875 --> 00:13:03,875
The Mugen is at its limit.

187
00:13:03,958 --> 00:13:06,875
I can't afford another
direct hit from his attack.

188
00:13:06,958 --> 00:13:11,083
[SKINN] I'll never forgive it!
I'll never forgive.

189
00:13:11,166 --> 00:13:13,500
I'll never forgive!

190
00:13:13,583 --> 00:13:15,750
The door's right behind me!

191
00:13:21,208 --> 00:13:22,458
Mugen!

192
00:13:25,083 --> 00:13:27,000
[KANDA]
Will you hold?

193
00:13:27,083 --> 00:13:29,375
[KANDA grunts]
Nigen Swords!

194
00:13:31,166 --> 00:13:35,958
I'll never forgive.
I'll never forgive.

195
00:13:36,041 --> 00:13:37,833
I'll never forgive it.

196
00:13:37,916 --> 00:13:44,000
I'll never forgive...
you Exorcists!

197
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:50,625
[KANDA] He'll destroy the exit.
We have no choice, Mugen!

198
00:13:50,708 --> 00:13:52,625
Sangen Style!

199
00:13:55,958 --> 00:13:59,833
[KANDA] Take my life force
and grow strong. Mugen!

200
00:14:16,208 --> 00:14:21,208
[KANDA grunts]

201
00:14:24,791 --> 00:14:28,541
[grunting continues]

202
00:14:28,625 --> 00:14:31,416
You can bear it. Mugen!

203
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:35,541
[SKINN shouts]

204
00:14:35,625 --> 00:14:38,333
[KANDA shouts]

205
00:14:43,625 --> 00:14:46,208
[KANDA] He's becoming
even more powerful!

206
00:14:46,291 --> 00:14:48,208
But there's nothing left of him!

207
00:14:48,291 --> 00:14:50,541
