00:14:57,541 --> 00:15:01,791
[SKINN] I'll never forgive.
I'll never forgive Innocence!

210
00:15:01,875 --> 00:15:03,833
Never!

211
00:15:03,916 --> 00:15:09,125
[KANDA] So this is it.
The legendary rage of Noah.

212
00:15:09,208 --> 00:15:12,083
I'll never forgive!

213
00:15:12,166 --> 00:15:15,500
We are Noah. Immortal.

214
00:15:15,583 --> 00:15:19,708
You are human. And will die!

215
00:15:21,000 --> 00:15:25,916
[KANDA]
Death. I refuse it. Not until...

216
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:29,375
...I find the one
I'm searching for.

217
00:15:34,541 --> 00:15:38,041
[KANDA gasps]

218
00:15:50,833 --> 00:15:53,583
[SKINN sighs]
I did it.

219
00:15:53,666 --> 00:15:58,708
