Innocence into pieces!

224
00:16:28,416 --> 00:16:33,166
[laughing continues]

225
00:16:34,583 --> 00:16:37,416
[SKINN] Huh? That beam
of light nearly hit me.

226
00:16:37,500 --> 00:16:40,833
But what the hell was it?
Not an attack.

227
00:16:40,916 --> 00:16:43,708
No way. I destroyed
his Innocence!

228
00:16:43,791 --> 00:16:44,625
[KANDA]
Mugen.

229
00:16:44,708 --> 00:16:45,708
[SKINN gasps]

230
00:16:45,791 --> 00:16:47,291
[KANDA]
Absorb.

231
00:17:03,958 --> 00:17:06,291
Impossible! The light!

232
00:17:06,375 --> 00:17:09,291
