pieces of Innocence!

233
00:17:09,375 --> 00:17:12,208
Joining them together!

234
00:17:12,291 --> 00:17:15,291
[KANDA] This technique
is called Sangen Style.

235
00:17:15,375 --> 00:17:17,250
It feeds off my life.

236
00:17:17,333 --> 00:17:23,750
If I'm not dead. That means,
my sword isn't either.

237
00:17:23,833 --> 00:17:25,250
[SKINN gasps]

238
00:17:39,583 --> 00:17:41,041
[gasps]

239
00:17:41,125 --> 00:17:44,916
[KANDA yells]

240
00:17:55,125 --> 00:17:58,208
[KANDA]
It's done.

241
00:17:58,291 --> 00:18:00,333
This battle is finished.

242
00:18:08,166 --> 00:18:12,875
[grunts] You still
don't get it, Exorcist?

243
00:18:12,958 --> 00:18:18,375
I already told you.
The Noah are immortal!

244
00:18:18,458 --> 00:18:21,333
I'm not done!
Nothing's finished yet!

245
00:18:21,416 --> 00:18:24,041
Far from it!

246
00:18:24,125 --> 00:18:28,375
But why are you still alive?
Damn Exorcist!

247
00:18:28,458 --> 00:18:32,000
And how were you able to
survive my attacks this long?

248
00:18:32,083 --> 00:18:34,250
[KANDA]
I already told you.

249
00:18:34,333 --> 00:18:37,791
[SKINN]
I see... You are... You're...

250
00:18:37,875 --> 00:18:41,541
[SKINN groans]

251
00:18:41,625 --> 00:18:45,541
This battle is concluded.
So shut up and die.

252
00:18:48,958 --> 00:18:52,208
[KANDA grunts] I'm going
have to grovel with Komui

253
00:18:52,291 --> 00:18:54,166
to put you back together.

254
00:19:05,500 --> 00:19:08,208
[LENALEE]
Make sure you catch up with us!

255
00:19:08,291 --> 00:19:11,458
[KANDA]
I wish... I could.

256
00:19:43,375 --> 00:19:45,750
[KANDA grunts]

257
00:19:47,125 --> 00:19:50,875
There's still... so much.

258
00:20:13,041 --> 00:20:18,000
[KANDA] Heh. Regardless, they're
gonna give me hell over this.

259
00:20:18,083 --> 00:20:19,666
[chuckles]

260
00:20:22,833 --> 00:20:26,083
[rumbling]

261
00:20:26,166 --> 00:20:27,750
What's that sound?

262
00:20:27,833 --> 00:20:29,208
Huh?

263
00:20:33,333 --> 00:20:36,541
[MIRANDA gasps]
Did anyone else feel that.

264
00:20:38,541 --> 00:20:41,083
Someone's time has run out.

265
00:20:42,375 --> 00:20:44,208
They've disappeared.

266
00:20:56,041 --> 00:21:01,000
♪

267
00:22:27,458 --> 00:22:29,375
[ALLEN] Believing Kanda
will soon join us,

268
00:22:29,458 --> 00:22:32,083
we continue our efforts
to escape the Ark.

269
00:22:32,166 --> 00:22:35,000
However, many obstacles
remain in our way.

270
00:22:35,083 --> 00:22:36,875
Devices that could have
only been thought up

271
00:22:36,958 --> 00:22:39,166
by a twisted mind. Or two.

272
00:22:39,250 --> 00:22:43,041
On the next D. Gray-Man:
"The Twins' Traps."

273
00:22:43,125 --> 00:22:46,291
Bring forth salvation to
this poor Akuma's soul!

274
00:22:47,708 --> 00:22:50,791
Hey you guys. Anyone seen Kanda?

